# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:15
translate portuguese micha10_53d7eff6:

    # "She gets in my car and we drive back towards the school and park near the dorms."
    "Ela entra no meu carro e dirigimos de volta para a escola, estacionando perto dos dormitórios."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:18
translate portuguese micha10_0ba0ce57:

    # mc "Would you walk to my dorm with me?"
    mc "Acompanhas-me até ao meu dormitório?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:19
translate portuguese micha10_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:26
translate portuguese micha10_fc5b71e7:

    # "We walk through the school courtyard, towards her dorm building."
    "Atravessamos o pátio da escola, em direção ao edifício do dormitório dela."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:27
translate portuguese micha10_9c8bddba:

    # "The night air is cool, and the school is surprisingly peaceful and quiet."
    "O ar da noite está fresco e a escola está surpreendentemente tranquila e silenciosa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:34
translate portuguese micha10_8f3659cb:

    # "She glances over at me and then slides her hand into mine."
    "Ela olha para mim e depois desliza a mão na minha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:35
translate portuguese micha10_b17081d9:

    # "Her hand is cold and small and soft. I hold it gently as we continue walking."
    "A mão dela é fria, pequena e macia. Seguro-a gentilmente enquanto continuamos a caminhar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:42
translate portuguese micha10_9207436c:

    # mc "Would you maybe want to sit and chat for a while before I go inside?"
    mc "Talvez queiras sentar-te e conversar um pouco antes de eu entrar?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:43
translate portuguese micha10_8fefe090:

    # mc "I had such a good time with you today. I am not quite ready for it to end."
    mc "Diverti-me imenso contigo hoje. Ainda não estou pronta para que isto acabe."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:44
translate portuguese micha10_4476e592:

    # pc "Sure, we can do that."
    pc "Claro, podemos fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:51
translate portuguese micha10_d96ba613:

    # "We sit on the bench together, her hand still enveloped in mine."
    "Sentamo-nos juntos no banco, a mão dela ainda envolvida na minha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:52
translate portuguese micha10_5e2207f4:

    # "I wonder what she would want to talk about? She barely talks about anything at all."
    "O que será que ela vai querer falar? Ela quase não fala de nada."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:59
translate portuguese micha10_5ec89b3b:

    # mc "I like it here."
    mc "Gosto daqui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:60
translate portuguese micha10_00ff76ff:

    # pc "Yeah, the fresh air feels really nice. And the trees are pretty."
    pc "Sim, o ar fresco é muito agradável. E as árvores são bonitas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:61
translate portuguese micha10_277d368d:

    # mc "No. I meant I like it here... in America."
    mc "Não. Queria dizer que gosto daqui... da América."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:62
translate portuguese micha10_193e6392:

    # mc "I wish that I could stay."
    mc "Quem me dera poder ficar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:69
translate portuguese micha10_4354fa16:

    # pc "What do you mean? You have to go back to Korea?"
    pc "O que queres dizer? Tens de voltar para a Coreia?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:71
translate portuguese micha10_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:72
translate portuguese micha10_b63541c5:

    # mc "Yes. I have to return and become married after I finish this semester."
    mc "Sim. Tenho de voltar e casar depois de terminar este semestre."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:73
translate portuguese micha10_1ae5f5f0:

    # pc "What? Why?"
    pc "O quê? Porquê?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:74
translate portuguese micha10_97c2ea57:

    # mc "My parents have arranged it. They have chosen a man. I will become his wife when I return."
    mc "Os meus pais arranjaram tudo. Escolheram um homem. Vou tornar-me sua esposa quando voltar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:75
translate portuguese micha10_29f911d6:

    # pc "Is that what you want? Do you even like him?"
    pc "É isso que queres? Pelo menos gostas dele?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:76
translate portuguese micha10_e1f07ca9:

    # mc "I have never met him. I am sure that he is nice though. My parents chose him."
    mc "Nunca o conheci. Mas tenho a certeza de que é simpático. Foram os meus pais que o escolheram."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:77
translate portuguese micha10_51e20623:

    # pc "You want that though?"
    pc "Mas é isso que queres?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:78
translate portuguese micha10_4989970d:

    # mc "I want to be a wife, yes. But I do like it here."
    mc "Quero ser esposa, sim. Mas gosto mesmo de estar aqui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:79
translate portuguese micha10_22cefe33:

    # pc "Why don't you just stay then? Why don't you tell your parents no, and stay here?"
    pc "Então porque não ficas? Porque não dizes não aos teus pais e ficas aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:86
translate portuguese micha10_d64f1fa7:

    # mc "It does not work that way."
    mc "Não é assim que as coisas funcionam."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:89
translate portuguese micha10_14baa1d2:

    # mc "I really like you too, [pcname]."
    mc "Também gosto muito de ti, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:91
translate portuguese micha10_24676458:

    # mc "Yes, I guess so."
    mc "Sim, acho que sim."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:98
translate portuguese micha10_52765170:

    # "We grow silent again, looking up at the stars."
    "Ficamos em silêncio outra vez, a olhar para as estrelas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:99
translate portuguese micha10_9e978195:

    # "She has to go back to Korea after this semester. I doubt I would see her again."
    "Ela tem de voltar para a Coreia depois deste semestre. Duvido que a volte a ver."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:100
translate portuguese micha10_494d2b9e:

    # "I can't help but feel really sad about that."
    "Não consigo deixar de me sentir muito triste com isso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:107
translate portuguese micha10_06878b88:

    # "As we're watching the sky, a shooting star flies past. She gasps."
    "Enquanto observamos o céu, uma estrela cadente passa a voar. Ela suspira."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:108
translate portuguese micha10_05fba3d4:

    # mc "Oh! It's so beautiful."
    mc "Oh! É tão bonito."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:109
translate portuguese micha10_013ea0ef:

    # pc "You should make a wish."
    pc "Devias pedir um desejo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:110
translate portuguese micha10_9d8e700d:

    # mc "A wish?"
    mc "Um desejo?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:111
translate portuguese micha10_10994647:

    # pc "Yeah, when you see a shooting star, you make a wish and it might come true."
    pc "Sim, quando vês uma estrela cadente, pedes um desejo e talvez ele se realize."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:118
translate portuguese micha10_74c726d2:

    # "She looks at me and speaks in a low, shy voice."
    "Ela olha para mim e fala com uma voz baixa e tímida."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:120
translate portuguese micha10_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/micha_10_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_10_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:121
translate portuguese micha10_c0a252cf:

    # mc "I wish you would kiss me."
    mc "Desejo que me beijes."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:122
translate portuguese micha10_2b10aa09:

    # pc "Oh. Well you're not supposed to tell anybody, or it won't happen."
    pc "Oh. Bem, não deves contar a ninguém, ou não vai acontecer."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:123
translate portuguese micha10_23b76a7a:

    # mc "Oh... I did not know that."
    mc "Oh... Não sabia disso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:139
translate portuguese micha10kiss_4cdfc044:

    # "I lean in and kiss her."
    "Inclino-me e beijo-a."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:140
translate portuguese micha10kiss_ca40b1c0:

    # pc "It's just dumb superstition anyway."
    pc "De qualquer forma, é só uma superstição parva."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:141
translate portuguese micha10kiss_39894277:

    # "At first, she is stiff, not moving at all as I kiss her lips. It's like kissing a mannequin."
    "No início, ela está rígida, sem se mexer enquanto beijo os seus lábios. É como beijar um manequim."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:154
translate portuguese micha10kiss_4319b810:

    # "But then I feel her body loosen, she puts her hand on my arm and leans in further, her lips moving against mine, breath coming quicker."
    "Mas depois sinto o corpo dela relaxar, ela coloca a mão no meu braço e inclina-se ainda mais, os lábios dela a moverem-se contra os meus, a respiração a acelerar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:155
translate portuguese micha10kiss_b9bbd6df:

    # "We kiss like that, under the stars, until the moment turns into minutes, and time seems to float away on the cool night breeze."
    "Beijamo-nos assim, sob as estrelas, até que o momento se transforma em minutos, e o tempo parece flutuar na brisa fresca da noite."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:167
translate portuguese micha10kiss_a2abceb1:

    # "I have no idea how much time has passed when she finally, reluctantly, pulls away."
    "Não faço ideia de quanto tempo passou quando ela finalmente, com relutância, se afasta."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:168
translate portuguese micha10kiss_e9b48769:

    # mc "I should go."
    mc "Tenho de ir."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:169
translate portuguese micha10kiss_7cf89165:

    # pc "You have to?"
    pc "Tens de ir?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:170
translate portuguese micha10kiss_1145978d:

    # mc "Yes, I apologize."
    mc "Sim, peço desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:173
translate portuguese micha10kiss_d89f8402:

    # pc "I should probably go home."
    pc "Provavelmente devia ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:174
translate portuguese micha10kiss_2148e939:

    # mc "Okay. Me too then."
    mc "Está bem. Eu também, então."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:186
translate portuguese micha10kiss_53fd2d63:

    # mc "I had a very good time tonight, [pcname]. Thank you."
    mc "Diverti-me imenso esta noite, [pcname]. Obrigado."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:187
translate portuguese micha10kiss_445c1419:

    # pc "I'm glad. I did too."
    pc "Fico contente. Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:188
translate portuguese micha10kiss_7aea7a63:

    # mc "I hope we can do this again soon."
    mc "Espero que possamos repetir isto em breve."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:190
translate portuguese micha10kiss_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/micha_goodnight1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_goodnight1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:191
translate portuguese micha10kiss_9b0423ef:

    # mc "Good night."
    mc "Boa noite."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:192
translate portuguese micha10kiss_c2ed5d6f:

    # pc "Good night, Mi-Cha."
    pc "Boa noite, Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:195
translate portuguese micha10kiss_17735f99:

    # "With that, she goes inside of her dorm building and I walk back to my car and drive away."
    "Dito isto, ela entra no edifício do dormitório e eu volto para o meu carro e vou-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:196
translate portuguese micha10kiss_de8a7413:

    # "Maybe Mi-Cha and I will only get the rest of the semester together, but we'll be sure to make it count."
    "Talvez a Mi-Cha e eu só tenhamos o resto do semestre juntos, mas vamos garantir que vale a pena."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:3
    old "Take Mi-Cha on more dates by calling her in the evening. Eventually she will ask you to walk her back to her dorm after one."
    new "Convida a Mi-Cha para mais encontros ligando-lhe à noite. Eventualmente, ela vai pedir-te para a acompanhares até ao dormitório depois da uma."

    # game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:4
    old "Take your opportunity and kiss her when the moment arises."
    new "Aproveita a oportunidade e beija-a quando surgir o momento."

    # game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:88
    old "That sucks, because I really like you"
    new "Isso é uma pena, porque gosto mesmo de ti"

    # game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:90
    old "I guess we're just temporary friends then, huh?"
    new "Acho que somos apenas amigos temporários, então, não é?"

    # game/Scenes/Micha/micha10.rpy:172
    old "Tell her good night"
    new "Diz-lhe boa noite"

